Archer spells: 
Spell 1; Roped Arrow  Info: basically a grappling hook. Upgrades: 
Tier I: First one, you just fly against the arrow when it hits something and deals 50% damage
Tier II: Same as tier I but deals 75% damage and pushes mobs back. 
Tier III: Same as the above. But arrows explodes where the roped arrow land. The arrows that explodes does 20%
Tier IV: Same as above. Arrow does 100% Arrow goes through mobs.
Tier V: Same as above. When you arrive to the arrow you shot you jump up in the air a bit. You also recieves Speed II for 1 min.

Spell 2; Homing Arrow Info: Fires an arrow that tracks an opinion down.
Tier I: Arrow tracks mobs and deal 150% damage. Arrow travels 20 blocks 
Tier II: Arrow explodes on impact and deals 175%. Arrow travels 30 blocks
Tier III: Same as above. When mobs are hit by the explosion, they fly up a few blocks and explodes again. 175% + 25% Travel 50 blocks
Tier IV: Same as above. But fires 2 arrows. Last arrow doesnt launch the player and it does 50% more Travel 50 blocks
Tier V: Same as above. But the last arrow launches the player down into the ground which causes another explosion which deals 25%. The attack deals 275% Travels 60 damage

Spell 3; Arrow Barrage Info: Fires a lot of arrows
Tier I: Shoots 10 arrows which deals 10%. 
Tier II: Shoots 20 arrows in a cone shape wich deals 5%.
Tier III: Shoots 30 arrows forwards. And 10 arrows around you. 5%
Tier IV: Same as above. 5 arrows orbit around you as a shield the arrows pushes enemies back.
Tier V: Instead of only shooting 10 arrows around you, it now shoots 20. 

Spell 4; Hunter's Companion Info: A wolf mob is spawned and walks forwards and bites foes in its path.
Tier I: Summons a wolf that launches forwards and bites your foes. Deals 100%. Wolf walks 2 blocks
Tier II: The wolf jumps forwards faster and jumps 5 blocks.
Tier III: The wolf bits mobs and drags them with it until the wolf disappears. 
Tier IV: Same as above but deals an extra bite before it disappears, dealing 50% more damage
Tier V: Same as above, wolf drags oponents and tackles them, dealing 100% more. The spell deals 250% all together. 
Summons a wolf when the attack is finished, that follow the summoner and attacks players dealing 50% per attack for 20 sec. 
